data.description: Such a sweet 3-bed, 2-bath ranch situated on a spacious .86-acre lot in Russiaville, 15 minutes outside of Kokomo, Indiana. This home has an attached 2-car garage and a nice large pole barn for extra storage or hobbies. With the flexibility of the laundry room in either the basement or one of the bedrooms, and the  space for a potential 4th bedroom, this property offers a lot of options! Don’t forget to check the agent remarks for details on the personal property included with the sale, and some items available for purchase.
